## API（Lite）
::TuffPropsTable
---
rows:
  - name: currentPage
    type: number
    default: '1'
    description: 当前页
  - name: pageSize
    type: number
    default: '10'
    description: 每页数量
  - name: total
    type: number
    default: '0'
    description: 总数量
  - name: showInfo
    type: boolean
    default: 'false'
    description: 显示总量信息
  - name: showFirstLast
    type: boolean
    default: 'false'
    description: 显示首末页按钮
---
:::

